snippet.title: Warcraft Remastered Battle Chest Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
The Warcraft Remastered Battle Chest Launch Trailer takes you on a journey 30 years in the making – like never before. Relive the legendary games that started an entire franchise, now remastered with all-new graphics, uprezzed sound, and quality of life upgrades. 

Purchase the Warcraft Remastered Battle Chest today and relive the beginning of a legacy. 

► Visit Warcraft on Battle.net: https://us.shop.battle.net/en-us/product/warcraft-remastered-battle-chest
--
► Follow Warcraft on Twitter: https://twitter.com/warcraft
